**pyesx module**

Python modules and routines associated with the Ecosystem Surface Exchange
Model (ESX) [Simpson & al (*unpublished*)]

This contains:

  **run**
  Routines to treat and visualise the results from ESX simulations

  **data**
  Routines to visualise, treat and format independent datafiles that can be used by the ESX model as inputs

  **simulation**
  Package to setup and run ESX simulations from python

  **utils**
  Tool functions

  **path**
  Package to navigate in the ESX repository

  **analysis**
  Package to make easier the comparisons between modelled values and independent observations

  **lib**
  Libraries of data and global variables

